race.comment: FROTHING (4) settled close the lead but was checked in the run and turned spotting a start, winding up strongly to place (31.04) at this track over 520m in a Maiden. Can find winning form here. IMPRESS NEMO (6) finished well back on debut when seventh (31.30) at this track over 520m. Can do far better this time. AUREATE (3) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd on October 29 over 520m at this track behind Zero Surf beaten 2.25 lengths (30.53) in a Maiden. Leading chance. HANNAH'S PASSION (1) missed the placings here on debut but is well-placed to make amends.
